HOST YOUR SPECIAL OCCASIONS
In Historic Style
The possibilities for your special event are endless at The Banyan Estate. As a special event venue in Malabar, Florida, we can accommodate events and parties of all types and sizes. Choose one of our individual rooms or reserve the entire estate for larger events. With luxury amenities and historic charm, The Banyan Estate is the perfect backdrop for a beautiful, stress-free occasion. Schedule a venue tour today!
Venue Amenities
12-foot ceilings throughout
Dimmable chandeliers
Exposed rafters in Pavilion
Original historic windows
Handcrafted hardwood floors
On-site venue manager
Complimentary assisted parking
On-site ceremony options
Bridal prep rooms
Prep kitchen
On-site parking
Linens, chargers, and other decor
Setup and teardown
House tables & chairs for up to 150 guests
BREVARD COUNTY EVENT VENUE
FOR ALL OCCASIONS
Events and Celebrations
Baby showers, bridal showers, engagement parties, memorial services, reunions, local festivals, expos, trade shows, corporate events, and much more!
Collaborations At The Banyan Estate
Styled shoots at The Banyan Estate are accepted on a case by case basis. Please contact us and send us photos of your work so we can make sure we are a good fit.
“What an awesome place for any event. Had the best time there this weekend and the owners Tom and Joanne are awesome, dynamic people. The venue is gorgeous and the grounds are fantastic. You want to have your next event here, that’ts for sure… don’t miss out.”
